mooege's focus is entirely on education, and we would like to keep it that way.
Since any public and/or commercial use of this software is considered illegal in many countries (please refer to your local law), the mooege team will not provide any help nor support with such usage in any way. Every user of this software is encouraged to make sure no law is being broken in his/her country.
